sentences.english: You shouldnt have done this. I just did what I should have done.
sentences.chinese: 你不用这样，我只是做了分内该做的事情。

sentences.english: To do your duty is not enough. You must go the extra mile.
sentences.chinese: 只满足于分内事是不够的，你必须多做一点点。

sentences.english: That’s Jupiter doing its cosmic job, astronomers like to say.
sentences.chinese: 天文学家说啊，木星在太空上班，这是它分内的事。

sentences.english: It has colored domes inside and clear domes outside.
sentences.chinese: 分内有色罩或两色相配，外白鲨透明两层。

sentences.english: It's her duty to look after her aunt.
sentences.chinese: 照顾她姨妈是她分内的事。

sentences.english: Pay attention to their fair share of oil gas hole size, and the design of the gas points capacity.
sentences.chinese: 注意气分内回油孔尺寸，还有气分的设计容积。

sentences.english: Everyone was doing their part and she was volunteering at the hospital down­town.
sentences.chinese: 每个人都做着分内之事，她在镇中心的医院义务服务。

sentences.english: But possesses all these, actually all is government official's duty-bound matter.
sentences.chinese: 但所有这一切，其实都是政府官员的分内事。

sentences.english: It is part of your duty to proof twenty pages.
